<div class="com-share" data-id="22857" data-title="《在曼谷可以用 Uber 叫小摩托了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22857/medium/22857.jpg?1456386559" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22857.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
